channel.title: || F2P-PVP || Unique & Different!
channel.description:
[center]NEW New skulls (orginal) Combat has been flawed No more running up with mage and range 20% Damage amulet works New thieving system Kills and deaths are now proper VOTE4CASH SYSTEM (500k) More to come New interface [img]http://s8.postimg.org/4qr2gp68l/Untitled.png[/img] [/center]
[center][b]2GP RAM VPS[/b]
[img]http://s14.postimg.org/51iahvjep/Untitled.png[/img][/center]
[center] [img]http://s13.postimg.org/k9lun499z/logo.png[/img]
[img]http://static1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20130524005607/2007scape/images/4/4a/Skull.png[/img] [b] F2P PVP Server[/b] [img]http://static1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20130524005607/2007scape/images/4/4a/Skull.png[/img]
[img]http://s10.postimg.org/q7toriwjd/coollogo_com_10767316.png[/img]
[img]http://s28.postimg.org/5fsfixvgt/image.png[/img] --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- [b][font=Typewriter][SIZE=4]First off, welcome to F2P-PVP. This server is dedicated to my old memories of oldschool runescape F2P PK'ing. I made this server because i know there are others that would enjoy some of the unique content that will be implemented every couple of days. This will be my main priority and i will promise to do my best, so YOU will be satisfied. I hope you give the game a try![/SIZE][/font][/b] ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
